	 <title>System.CreateDeviceUserWithEncryptedPassword</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para>This operator creates a mapping from the Dataphor user to the Device
		  user. This allows Dataphor users to connect to devices using their own level of
		  protection. This Operator can only be used by the Admin users. An encrypted
		  password must be used with this operator. AConnectionString can be specified if
		  a unique connection string is required.</para> 
	 <example> 
		  <title>Example</title> 
		  <programlisting>CreateUser("JS1", "John Smith", "Password");
create device Linter
	class "Alphora.Dataphor.DAE.Device.Linter.LinterDevice,AlphoraLinterDevice";
select EncryptPassword("DevicePassword");
CreateDeviceUserWithEncrypedPassword
  ("JS1", "Linter", "SYSTEM", "ENOq2MyVfW04WwuFthdVmu4=");</programlisting> 
		  <programlisting>ENOq2MyVfW04WwuFthdVmu4=</programlisting> 
	 </example> 
